# Linux Configuration

## Commands

- `colors`: Lists ANSI color codes and displays the associated colors

- `hpScreen`: Configures xrandr with the appropriate parameters for my
  HP2159m

- `yakuakeToggle`: Toggles the yakuake drop down toggle

## Configuration

- `bashrc`: Sets Bash options and sources the following files

  - `prompt`: Configures prompt

  - `aliases`: Sets useful aliases

  - `screen`: Useful shell functions for interacting with `screen`

  - `venv_activte`: Useful shell functions for interacting with python `venv`

- `Xmodmap`: Sets capslock to escape

- `pretty-git-prompt.yml`: Configures pretty git prompt

## Installs

- `rust`

- `the-fuck`

- `pretty-git-prompt`
